<HL>
   Bush Moves Toward Economic Sanctions
   In Bid to Cut Soviet Pressure on Lithuania
   ----
   By Michel McQueen
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/23/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9E
</SO>
<CO>
   FREST
</CO>
